{"tid":2409033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支那呢個名詞起源於古印度","createTime":"2021-02-15T12:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T12:50:07.000Z","uid":327169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0a19ac5f59872346606bb059666514485a265a","tid":2409033,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"「支那」起源於印度。印度古代人稱中國為chini，據說是「秦」的音譯。中國從印度引進梵文佛經，高僧按照音譯就把chini翻譯成「支那」或「至那」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那人民共和國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁為乜中日戰爭後，支國人唔認自己係支那? 因為要仇恨日本? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b187ec6a24b94b308624a5730782857c2e85d0b8","tid":2409033,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"印度一點都不能少"},{"pid":"0be26ea415f6497926378ff7fb30d02c3a2e7357","tid":2409033,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNmoxjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNmoxjx.jpg&h=97cac758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那"}]}